    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this fantastic find! This car is in great shape and has been well-cared for, making it a reliable and stylish choice for its next owner. It drives smoothly and looks wonderful, with only minor signs of regular use that show it's been loved. It's a solid, dependable vehicle that\u2019s ready for many more miles of adventures!",
